edu.kennesaw.cs4850.database

Interface GenericResultSet.ResultGatherer

  • Enclosing class:
    GenericResultSet

    public static interface GenericResultSet.ResultGatherer
    Interface definition to obtain information from the database specific table entry class. The ResultGather interface needs to overwrite these functions for the specific database when setting t new static interface.
